                  </hi>. My husband keeps a shop in New-street, Brompton. The prisoner came there at twenty minutes before ten o'clock at night, on the 15th of Dec, for two herrings, which came to 1 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>—he gave me a shilling—I gave him 10 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. change—after he was gone I looked at the shilling, and found it was bad—my husband went after him, and he wasbrought back—I am sure he is the man</p>
